        <abstract> 
<p>Criticises chapter on good effect of crossing in <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>: (1) does not accept that inbreeding alone results in degeneracy; (2) good effects of crossing exaggerated; (3) denies deleterious effects of close marriage in humans.</p> 
        </abstract>
